%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day2MorningP
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day2_morning_pill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Morning, Andy. We have another productive day ahead of us. Same stuff as
      yesterday. Fix some wiring over at the navigation room. Other than keeping
      DOLOS happy, do you have any questions?
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Yeah, I got some if you don\u2019t mind me asking."
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Fire away.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices:
    - choiceText: "The capsules\u2026 what\u2019s in them that makes them so mandatory
        to be taken every day?"
      nextLineIndex: 2
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: You never really talk about yourself, Al. What did you do before
        working for the DOLOS Corporation?
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: How do you feel about the DOLOS Corporation? From one employee
        to another?
      nextLineIndex: 18
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: I should probably get to work, actually.
      nextLineIndex: 26
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 1
    advanceToLine: 26
    repeat: 1
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It\u2019s a compound blend designed to mitigate the psychological effects
      of long-term isolation, radiation exposure, and circadian disruption."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Along with a mix of nootropics and other company-approved stimulants to
      boost productivity, of course.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 4
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Though I wonder, why ask that now of all times?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Well, it\u2019s my last year here before my contract expires.
        I wanted to make sure I wasn\u2019t breaking any niche rules before my term
        is over.It would look bad on my resume."
      nextLineIndex: 5
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: No reason in particular. Just a shower thought.
      nextLineIndex: 6
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "An ideal employee. It\u2019s wonderful that you adhere to company policy
      so diligently."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: You should know all this. Taking these medications is a part of your contract
      for working on the SUNSET16.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 7
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: It is in your best interest to take them every day. To keep you safe, of
      course.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "I\u2019m very familiar with our company policy. There\u2019s no
        need to worry."
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I was an electrical grid regulator for SinoEuro Power. Did that for 3 years
      before the company merged with NUSA Electric, not long after Erebus Holdings
      bought out the DOLOS Corporation.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 9
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Anyhow, they restructured and took away some of my benefits. I left and
      found a posting for the SUNSET16 not long after.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 10
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "And\u2026 here I am."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Sounds like quite the journey you went on. I\u2019m impressed."
      nextLineIndex: 11
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I\u2019m surprised you left. I always took you for a corporate
        loyalist."
      nextLineIndex: 15
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "On paper, maybe. But there\u2019s less chaos here."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 12
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I was never really one to bounce from corporation to corporation. I did
      my job and did it well.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 13
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "In a way, you\u2019re like that too. That\u2019s why you passed the screenings
      when applying and got your job here."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 14
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Life coasts on by when you stick to the status quo. Remember that.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I was an opportunist at heart. Keyword was. It\u2019s just that SinoEuro
      Power provided some good benefits for me at the time."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 16
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "But\u2026 they pale in comparison to what the DOLOS Corporation provides
      me now."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 17
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I have no reason to leave the company any time soon. Neither should you.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Out of all the significant conglomerates and mega-corporations on the
      planet, without a doubt, the DOLOS Corporation is one of the most\u2026 secure."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 19
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "They\u2019ve been around for nearly forty years now."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "The company started as a small engineering firm in the 2080\u2019s, manufacturing
      automated systems for cargo vessels. Then the company pivoted, hard."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Pivoted into what?
      nextLineIndex: 21
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: A lot of stuff, eventually. DOLOS has its hands in a lot of pies.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 22
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: The Life-Sciences Division takes care of our collars, supplements, that
      sort of stuff.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 23
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: The Aerospace Division took care of things like the SUNSET16.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 24
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: They got a division for resource extraction. Mining operations on the Moon,
      asteroids, and a few spots on Mars.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 25
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s where most of the real money comes from. It\u2019s how they
      partially funded the SUNSET16 and our AI development before being bought by
      Erebus Holdings."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I think that\u2019s all I have time for too. Shorter chat than usual.
      I have work to complete."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices:
    - choiceText: Talk to you later.
      nextLineIndex: 27
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: 
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
